{"tid":532394,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)地心浩劫","createTime":"2018-01-17T20:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T21:53:28.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9477b12212afda03b41a1f7899a3bee61f4ecb6c","tid":532394,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T20:11:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=rf2Rgc6hJaqUPXdShLT%2BcMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=51b5ed12\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=rf2Rgc6hJaqUPXdShLT%2BcMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c78aa08b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4R6_QYkcPmo/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F4R6_QYkcPmo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=026f6108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影講述地球的核心因不明原因停止轉動，以致電磁場減弱。在失去地磁的保護下，地球會遭到致命的高能宇宙微波輻射襲擊，造成災難。此時有6人組成團隊，駕駛一艘名為「維吉爾號」的潛地艇，鑽進熾熱地函，放置並引爆核彈，使地核再次轉動...<br />\n<br />\n4 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=rf2Rgc6hJaqUPXdShLT%2BcMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b464a01e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=rf2Rgc6hJaqUPXdShLT%2BcMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=025ddaa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80db9c2b637aa8dc10d3f5ea1e3e4e5aa785979","tid":532394,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T20:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a343fa78c4a3a67706fae892b003b2260d340f7","tid":532394,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T20:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5630ed95391edcd9af7e484473b83a7fb6e54b3b","tid":532394,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T21:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}